column2: SELECT lcgID, ra_lcg, dec_lcg FROM MYDB.lista_all_galaxies OPEN my_cursor WHILE (# = #) BEGIN FETCH NEXT from my_cursor into @lcgID, @ra_lcg, @dec_lcg IF (@@fetch_status < #) break INSERT MYDB.LCG_objIDs SELECT @lcgID, p.objID as objID_lcg, p.ra, p.dec FROM dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (@ra_lcg, @dec_lcg, #) as n, PhotoObj as p WHERE n.objID = p.objID END CLOSE my_cursor DEALLOCATE my_cursor
